T1  - FEMINIZATION UNVEILED: MANAGEMENT QUALITIES IN CONTEMPORARY WRITINGS
AU  - Fondas, Nanette
Y1  - 1997/01/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1997.9707180266
