T1  - TOWARD UNDERSTANDING JOINT VENTURE PERFORMANCE AND SURVIVAL: A BARGAINING AND INFLUENCE APPROACH TO TRANSACTION COST THEORY
AU  - Pearce, Robert J.
Y1  - 1997/01/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/01/01
